'usuriousness.' The Sanskrit version has 'laziness,' as if Nêr. had read
âsû*d*akîh.

<span id="fn_567"></span>[106:2](sbe24065.htm#fr_575.md) Nêr. has read
*g*ahî, and translated 'incontinence.'

